name: THE WORLD
description:
Insights from the Dreaming Pool - Your world order is shifting.

Nourishing wise loving Gaia, Goddess, our Home. The Earth, nourishment. Magic, the creative circle out of which very thing is born. Giver of life, sustenance, together and united each effects the other. 

Sacred Center 

All elements coming together in your story. Balanced unity shows the promise of success. An ending of a difficult journey. Completion. The endless infinite nature of energy. Fulfilment, balance, attainment, illumination, accomplishment. The center of the world,  a microcosm of order known and settled.

The Dreaming Pool Oracle is a collaboration between artists Maia Mellier 🕸 🕷 (@maiamellier) & AEVIN (@aevin_io)
